Information
------------------------------
A documentary feature about world champion boxer Joe Calzaghe and his extraordinary father Enzo, who trained him throughout his 20-year career. Their journey started in a tin shed on the windswept hills of the Welsh valleys and ended under the bright lights of Madison Square Garden - fighting for a final payday that neither could have ever imagined. Featuring interviews with Michael J Fox, Matthew Rhys, James Dean Bradfield, Chris Eubank, Thomas Hauser and Mikkel Kessler.
